quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,33,"Si sa…óteende memii yim…ďe …ďeen, …ďe noddira Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe ruttitii…ďe e makko; refti si o mee…óinii …ďe yumeende immorde e makko, e jaka fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe no kafida e Joomi mun,"
  30,34,"Yo…ďe yeddu ko min ngokki …ďe kon. "Awa dakmitee, arma nganndon"."
  30,35,"Kaa Min njippin e ma…ď…ďe hujja (Deftere), hara honde yeewta fii ko …ďe cirkatnoo kon?"
  30,36,"Si Min mee…óinirii yim…ďe …ďen neema, …ďe weltoroo mo. Si bone memirii …ďe sabu ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardiniri kon, e jaka he…ďe ta∆īoo."
  30,37,"E …ďe nkiaani won'de Alla no yaacnana arsike on mo o muuyani, O …ďillina? Wonii e …óuum, Ma'andeeji wonan'de yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  30,38,"Jonnu jom-…ďadiido o hakke makko on, e …ďillii…ďe e …ďii-laawol. ∆äuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude wonan'de …ďeen faalaa…ďe yarluyee Alla on; ko …ďeen ngoni maloytee…ďe …ďen."
  30,39,"Kala ko njonnu…óon e riba, fii on …ďeydor e jaw…óe yim…ďe …ďen, …óuum …ďeydotaako ka Alla, kala non ko ngokku…óon e Jakka, mo faandori…óon welayee Alla, …ďen …óon, ko sowanoytee…ďe [njo…ďdi] …ďeen."
  30,40,"Ko Alla woni tak…óo on, refti o arsiki on, refti o wara on, refti o wuurnita on. Hara no e kafidaa…ói mon …óin wa…óay…ói go…ó…óum e …óum? Senayeewoo-dani Mo! O toowii e kon ko …ďe cirkata."
  30,41,"Bone on fee√Īiri ka njoorndi e ka maaje, sabu ko juu…óe yim…ďe …ďen faggitii kon; fii yo O mee…óin …ďe yoga e ko …ďe ngolli; mbelajo'o, …ďe nduttoto."